---
title: Onion Crunch Chicken with Mashed Sweet Potatoes, Roasted Green Beans & Dijonnaise
description: Crispy chicken + honey mustard is a match made in mealtime heaven. And because we’re all about making sure your mealtimes are heavenly, we took that classic combo and chef’d it up a bit (still making sure it’s on your table in 30). To start, chicken breasts are brushed with dijonnaise, then coated with a mixture of Monterey Jack and crushed fried onions. The chicken’s roasted to juicy perfection and served with creamy mashed sweet potatoes and roasted green beans. There’s more dijonnaise on the side for dunking and drizzling—because you deserve it.
